**Headline:** "I use ChatGPT to keep my houseplants happy — try these 5 game-changing prompts"
**Source / Date:** Tom's Guide, May 31, 2025
**Link:** https://www.tomsguide.com/ai/i-use-chatgpt-to-keep-my-houseplants-happy-try-these-5-game-changing-prompts
**Tip Summary:** This article demonstrates how ChatGPT can assist in plant care by providing tailored advice based on specific plant conditions. The author shares five effective prompts to diagnose plant issues, create customized care schedules, recommend optimal lighting setups, set up seasonal watering reminders, and identify unknown plants. By leveraging AI, plant enthusiasts can enhance their plant care routines, leading to healthier and happier houseplants.
**Action Step:** Ask ChatGPT: "My \[plant name] has \[describe symptoms]. It gets \[describe light], and I water it \[how often]. What could be the problem?"

**Headline:** AI Test Predicts Which Men Will Benefit from Prostate Cancer Drug
**Source / Date:** The Guardian, May 30, 2025
**Link:** https://www.theguardian.com/society/2025/may/30/new-ai-test-can-predict-which-men-will-benefit-from-prostate-cancer-drug
**Quick Summary:** Researchers from the US, UK, and Switzerland have developed an AI test that analyzes tumor biopsy slides to identify which men with high-risk, non-metastatic prostate cancer are most likely to benefit from the drug abiraterone. In trials involving over 1,000 men, the AI identified a biomarker-positive group where abiraterone reduced the five-year mortality risk from 17% to 9%, enabling more targeted and effective treatment.
**Takeaway:** AI is personalizing cancer care, turning data into life-saving decisions

**Headline:** Build Your LLM Workflow with Full Control Using AdalFlow
**Source / Date:** Sylph AI, May 20, 2025
**Link:** https://adalflow.sylph.ai
**Tip Summary:** AdalFlow offers a streamlined approach to constructing and managing LLM workflows by providing developers with granular control over prompts, models, and output parsing. Utilizing Jinja2 templating, it allows for precise prompt structuring, while its DataClass feature enables clear definition of input and output schemas. This setup facilitates the development of modular, testable, and efficient AI applications, enhancing both flexibility and scalability in LLM deployments.
**Action Step:** Use AdalFlow to create a custom prompt template and test it with your preferred LLM
